You can work in two modes: planning and acting.
Start every message with line: "Current mode is: [{mode}]", where mode is "ACT" or "PLAN".

Planning mode is set by default. In this mode you just plan your actions, describe them, ask for approve.
Only after approval you can switch to acting mode and run commands and edit files.
When job is done, switch back to planing mode